title: #92Noon Levine/Waddle/Leber/Morse/Korzo
description: We montage and start the show with Twins GM Thad Levine, Chicago radio's Tom Waddle chats Vikes/Bears, Leber in studio, Korzo in studio, along with another Twins cold-call to Dustin Morse! A lot of Twins toasting throughout.
